{"tid":1701460,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小心煽動","createTime":"2019-11-09T05:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T11:15:40.000Z","uid":276674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c049c3978d639b846d322ecc2560308f996ea114","tid":1701460,"uid":276674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"周同學一死，即刻有議員被捕、因姦受孕、圍醫院、CarCam 車主被捕、燒法院的消息。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知係唔係全部都係真，我亦無意話咩行動係啱，咩係唔啱。<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講，周同學一死就突然咁多消息，係唔係有人想引大家出嚟玩鑊勁嘅，然後就有藉口取消區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n大家要諗下要達到咩目標。要保區選，唔係要血債票償、唔係要俾泛民議員d咩，而係要唔俾建制議員有控制區議會同地區事務嘅機會。要區選係要打擊建制。<br />\n<br />\n無左區議會，政府名正言順唔聽地區民意處理地區事務。俾建制贏一樣。唯有民主派贏區選先係剝建制栅牙嘅第一步。<br />\n<br />\n所以夢遊前諗下發咩夢、點發、同幾時醒。"},{"pid":"57e6af1c2d493bfcf7e0b9c2ca4de50f324061ec","tid":1701460,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"好撚驚？"},{"pid":"88730effecf5323942b6491ef6be163cba306d4d","tid":1701460,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"屌 同路人9UP下姐  唔好咁多幻想"},{"pid":"8f3b83ab9de3e008c5d606d9a849064c698622bf","tid":1701460,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"***眾籌***<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先52%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=ee04fb39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=a0102eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8aafec78d28ef2858d4ae9b1bbbac63e87f896","tid":1701460,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"建制泛民<br />\n漢奸共匪<br />\n全部唔選"}]}